Context:
The Graphic Design program at George Brown College is offered either ONLINE (via webinar) or IN-PERSON. Interested individuals can sign up for an information session to learn more about the program and be kept updated on application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, and tours. The contact person for inquiries is Nicole Dimson, whose email address is ndimson@georgebrown.ca.

Additional contacts:
- Phone number: 416-415-2000
- TTY number: 1-877-515-5559
- Email inquiry: ask.george@georgebrown.ca

The college's website contains information subject to change without notice. It is recommended that students verify George Brown College fee requirements.
